  "_crew_bounty_note": "crews[].total_prime leaks two more French words — 'inconnu' (unknown, 31 crews) and 'aucune' (none, the ASL crew) — plus two malformed numbers. The Arlong crew is '42.5000.000', repaired to 42,500,000. Baroque Works is '399.700.00', which is missing a digit and could be 399,700,000 or 39,970,000: we refuse to guess and store null. Refusing to guess IS the feature.",
