  "_size_overrides_note": "Sizes are centimetres. '352cl' (Doc Q) is centilitres — a unit error upstream, so we refuse to guess and store null. '\\\"' (Vegapunk) is a stray quote character. '35km' (Zunesh) is real: it is a continent-sized elephant, converted here to 3,500,000 cm so the field stays one unit."
